title: Saucy Tex-Mex Chicken & Bacon Potato Top Pie with Hidden Veggies & Corn
description: Turn a juicy chicken drizzled in a creamy corn and veggie sauce into a veggie chicken pie, topped with potato. You can smell the Tex-Mex seasoning coming off the pie as it bakes, that’s when dinner gets very exciting, so dig in and enjoy!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

